.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ce0df6a2d9ed73946dc36d8a9d20573?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ce0df6a2d9ed73946dc36d8a9d20573?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ce0df6a2d9ed73946dc36d8a9d20573?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1534237929, "last_modified": 1534237929}, "last_reply_by": "nyfwan123", "last_touched": 1715666727, "title": "鬼压床，你们怎么解？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1040468", "created": 1715648356, "deleted": 0, "content": "也不是经常，但时不时会碰到，前几次还有点慌，现在只是烦。\r\n\r\n最神奇，我昨晚居然开始画万字符念“南无阿迷托福”。神特么怎么回事，我这种无神论者也会搞这一套。", "content_rendered": "<p>也不是经常，但时不时会碰到，前几次还有点慌，现在只是烦。</p>\n<p>最神奇，我昨晚居然开始画万字符念“南无阿迷托福”。神特么怎么回事，我这种无神论者也会搞这一套。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1715648356, "replies": 112, "id": 1040468}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 62709, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8958, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 402229, "username": "ynexz", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ynexz", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ad5c5e77d72942b8f362b009be30272?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ad5c5e77d72942b8f362b009be30272?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ad5c5e77d72942b8f362b009be30272?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1555400115, "last_modified": 1715583822}, "last_reply_by": "ConnectException", "last_touched": 1715665297, "title": "求推荐已通过实践稳妥的 Mini 迷你小主机解决方案", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1040291", "created": 1715586915, "deleted": 0, "content": "#### 机器主要用途\r\n\r\n   - 软路由\r\n   - 打算跑 PVE\r\n   - 使用 ZFS 提供存储（或者其他支持快照的存储）\r\n   - 跑各种服务，比如 Jellyfin 、PT 、Syncthing 、下载等等\r\n   - 编译任务、Android 、内核、node 等等各种\r\n\r\n\r\n#### 个人一些要求\r\n\r\n   1. 质量靠谱，能长期 7x24 稳定运行\r\n   2. 低功耗\r\n   3. 支持 IPMI 远程管理\r\n   4. 至少 2.5G 网口 ≥2 ，10G 最好\r\n   5. 支持 WiFi6 或 WiFi7\r\n   6. CPU 虚拟化 VT-x 、虚拟化直通 VT-d 支持，AES 全支持；(可有可无)支持 Intel vPro/AMD PRO\r\n   7. 内存 ≥ 16GB , ECC 最好\r\n   8. 硬盘位至少 3.5x6 ，m2x2, 2.5 硬盘位可选，有最好\r\n   9. 整机硬件完美兼容 Linux 主流发行版（如：Arch ，Gentoo ，Fedora 、Debian 等）\r\n   10. 整机硬件能较好的运行兼容黑苹果 （可选）\r\n   11. 便携式主机\r\n   \r\n   有成品最好, DIY 也行。预算￥ 2000", "content_rendered": "<h4>机器主要用途</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>软路由</li>\n<li>打算跑 PVE</li>\n<li>使用 ZFS 提供存储（或者其他支持快照的存储）</li>\n<li>跑各种服务，比如 Jellyfin 、PT 、Syncthing 、下载等等</li>\n<li>编译任务、Android 、内核、node 等等各种</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>个人一些要求</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>质量靠谱，能长期 7x24 稳定运行</li>\n<li>低功耗</li>\n<li>支持 IPMI 远程管理</li>\n<li>至少 2.5G 网口 ≥2 ，10G 最好</li>\n<li>支持 WiFi6 或 WiFi7</li>\n<li>CPU 虚拟化 VT-x 、虚拟化直通 VT-d 支持，AES 全支持；(可有可无)支持 Intel vPro/AMD PRO</li>\n<li>内存 ≥ 16GB , ECC 最好</li>\n<li>硬盘位至少 3.5x6 ，m2x2, 2.5 硬盘位可选，有最好</li>\n<li>整机硬件完美兼容 Linux 主流发行版（如：Arch ，Gentoo ，Fedora 、Debian 等）</li>\n<li>整机硬件能较好的运行兼容黑苹果 （可选）</li>\n<li>便携式主机</li>\n</ol>\n<p>有成品最好, DIY 也行。预算￥ 2000</p>\n", "last_modified": 1715587021, "replies": 96, "id": 1040291}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1691642161", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1691642161", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 15393, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1691642161", "stars": 7360, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 655518, "username": "MillaMaxwell", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/MillaMaxwell", "webs